author: William A.
title: Prayers, protests and blocking of traffic at LAX over Trump’s immigration changes
text:
— Melinda Escobar (@melindaescobar) January 30, 2017 Proud to be part of #NoMuslimBanLAX with @WestLADemClub & throngs of supporters, raising our voices against Trump to proclaim, #NoBanNoWall ! pic.twitter.com/Q90qgQnBAt 
— Sandra Fluke (@SandraFluke) January 30, 2017 
And blocking of traffic: 
— Javier Panzar (@jpanzar) January 30, 2017 Wow. A friend stuck at LAX just sent me this. Protesters are walking on streets so NO TRAFFIC can get through. How is this productive?? pic.twitter.com/KXW1WAOM54 
— Kacey Montoya (@kaceymontoya) January 30, 2017 Protesters in this video claim they have completely blocked LAX… Making people miss their flights??! https://t.co/0nooze1sP1
